        </item>
        <item>
            <title>1.10</title>
            <description><![CDATA[
                <ul style="font-size:13px;"><li>New: The animating (Now Playing) label in the LCD display was completely rewritten and is now more efficient and provides additional functionality.</li><li>Update: You can now click on the Now Playing label to loop through the available metadata such as track title, artist name, or album title.</li><li>Update: Additional updates to localization in all supported languages.</li><li>Update: Additional updates to the Help Book. The Help Book is accessible through the Help menu.</li></ul>
            ]]></description>
            <pubDate>Wed, 05 Jan 2022 19:48:42 -0800</pubDate>
            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>11.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <enclosure url="https://marioaguzman.github.io/musicwidget/updater/Music%20Widget.zip" sparkle:version="12" sparkle:shortVersionString="1.10" length="4212250" type="application/octet-stream" sparkle:edSignature="K5gyJXC0einkY/mssrJeicFoOJxbUUgShG4fgvLhnRgqygxI/9h4aRnDdc8KgTqLn83zwYMjwNkMn/66kHm0Ag=="/>
        </item>
        <item>
            <title>1.11</title>
            <description><![CDATA[
                <ul style="font-size:13px;"><li>New: The volume ring from the original iTunes Dashboard widget is back! Drag vertically on the ring or scroll vertically within the ring's bounds to adjust volume.</li><li>New: Music Widget has additional keywords to make it more discoverable using Spotlight.</li><li>Fix: Addressed an issue where opening Music Widget would not initially display track information if streaming any Apple Music radio station.</li><li>Update: Adjusted the Preferences window for more a fluid display of content.</li><li>Update: There is now more topics in the Help Book including new information for adjusting volume and Dock Menu Items.</li></ul>
            ]]></description>
            <pubDate>Mon, 14 Feb 2022 20:53:13 -0800</pubDate>
            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>11.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
