        <item>
            <title>1.12</title>
            <description><![CDATA[
                <h4>Music Widget v1.12</h4><ul style="font-size:13px;"><li>Addresses an issue affecting the new Volume Ring UI introduced in v1.11. At times, when dragging the ring to adjust volume, it would get "caught" and prevent volume adjustments.</li></ul><h4>Music Widget 1.11</h4><ul style="font-size:13px;"><li>Fix: Fixes an issue where dragging the volume ring might get "caught".</li><li>New: The volume ring from the original iTunes Dashboard widget is back! Drag vertically on the ring or scroll vertically within the ring's bounds to adjust volume.</li><li>New: Music Widget has additional keywords to make it more discoverable using Spotlight.</li><li>Fix: Addressed an issue where opening Music Widget would not initially display track information if streaming any Apple Music radio station.</li><li>Update: Adjusted the Preferences window for more a fluid display of content.</li><li>Update: There is now more topics in the Help Book including new information for adjusting volume and Dock Menu Items.</li></ul>
            ]]></description>
            <pubDate>Wed, 16 Feb 2022 19:34:29 -0800</pubDate>
